@1 = ~You look to be a group of fine travelers. My name is Skeezer Lumpkin the VI. I'm on my way to the fine city of Baldur's Gate and looking for a group of fine travelers like yerselves to join up with. 'Tis far more safe to travel with a group than it is alone don't ye know!~
@2 = ~Welcome to ye. Always looking for a good hand at magic!~
@3 = ~I'm sorry, but we have no need for another hand right now.~
@4 = ~That's fine...very fine indeed. I'm a fair hand at magic and I like to tinker a bit. I won't disappoint ye!~
@5 = ~I understand. Perhaps next time?~
